title: #92Noon! DraftFodder/Florio/Twins/Miller/Lombardi
description: Show kicks off with "Freaks & Frauds," some players that look ready to shine in the NFL and a few others that may be overhyped. Florio's weekly spot, the Twins win all the time now, Lions Vox Dan Miller on his team's vibe into the weekend, NFL exec/SB winning Michael Lombardi with Draft opinions and more!
